  "detailed_description": "<strong>Colored Effects is a puzzle platformer game with unique handcrafted levels and a simple design. Play in this peaceful environment, solve puzzles and collect the gems to complete each level.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/6bbe52baa463d04a845eff86eb016e1b.poster.avif?t=1724320689\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/6bbe52baa463d04a845eff86eb016e1b.webm?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/6bbe52baa463d04a845eff86eb016e1b.mp4?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Colors and Effects</strong></h2>Effects are the abilities you use in the game, each effect is unique and distinguishable by its own color. Switching Colors at the right moment is the key to progress.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/10a18cb110dc7e82b7467d17566eaba5.poster.avif?t=1724320689\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/10a18cb110dc7e82b7467d17566eaba5.webm?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/10a18cb110dc7e82b7467d17566eaba5.mp4?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Bosses</strong></h2>Encounter bosses in between levels, each boss has unique attacks and requires a different way to defeat it.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/e1aa633fc019d5f2f38e4e7eb99e6491.poster.avif?t=1724320689\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/e1aa633fc019d5f2f38e4e7eb99e6491.webm?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/e1aa633fc019d5f2f38e4e7eb99e6491.mp4?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Restart and try again</strong></h2>You may die or get trapped in this game, nothing prevents you from restarting at any moment and getting back in an instant.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/c2e3b3be2db1a8ff24125703bd04ee4f.poster.avif?t=1724320689\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/c2e3b3be2db1a8ff24125703bd04ee4f.webm?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/c2e3b3be2db1a8ff24125703bd04ee4f.mp4?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Colored Effects is a puzzle platformer game with unique handcrafted levels and a simple design. Play in this peaceful environment, solve puzzles and collect the gems to complete each level.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/6bbe52baa463d04a845eff86eb016e1b.poster.avif?t=1724320689\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/6bbe52baa463d04a845eff86eb016e1b.webm?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/6bbe52baa463d04a845eff86eb016e1b.mp4?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Colors and Effects</strong></h2>Effects are the abilities you use in the game, each effect is unique and distinguishable by its own color. Switching Colors at the right moment is the key to progress.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/10a18cb110dc7e82b7467d17566eaba5.poster.avif?t=1724320689\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/10a18cb110dc7e82b7467d17566eaba5.webm?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/10a18cb110dc7e82b7467d17566eaba5.mp4?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Bosses</strong></h2>Encounter bosses in between levels, each boss has unique attacks and requires a different way to defeat it.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/e1aa633fc019d5f2f38e4e7eb99e6491.poster.avif?t=1724320689\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/e1aa633fc019d5f2f38e4e7eb99e6491.webm?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/e1aa633fc019d5f2f38e4e7eb99e6491.mp4?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Restart and try again</strong></h2>You may die or get trapped in this game, nothing prevents you from restarting at any moment and getting back in an instant.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/c2e3b3be2db1a8ff24125703bd04ee4f.poster.avif?t=1724320689\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/c2e3b3be2db1a8ff24125703bd04ee4f.webm?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892570/extras/c2e3b3be2db1a8ff24125703bd04ee4f.mp4?t=1724320689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
